      <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#9CA3AF;line-height:1.75;">Your focus is not a character trait. It is a neurochemical state. The dopaminergic system, the adenosinergic system, the mitochondria in your neurons: these are the mechanisms you are managing with this protocol. Thirty days of deliberate focus ritual, optimized caffeine timing, and consistent cellular energy support will change the quality of every session you train from this point forward. Not because you wanted it more. Because you built the system that makes it possible. Do the work with everything you have been given. That is the standard.</p>
